Package org.firewaterframework.rest

Class Summary
DocumentResponse This Response subclass implements it's payload as an XML document.
Method This class corresponds to the HTTP METHOD header argument in that protocol.
MIMEType This class represents the Media-type header field in an HTTP response.
Request This class is the Request object for the Firewater framework.
Response This class is responsible for result representation of a REST Request.
Status The HTTP STATUS response values.
StreamResponse This class wraps an unstructured byte stream to hold the response payload.
